videos.headline: Sun Devils strike first with 58-yard TD
videos.description: Arizona State WR N'Keal Harry catches screen pass and takes it all the way to the end zone.

videos.headline: 300-pound DT gets pick-6 for Sun Devils TD
videos.description: Arizona State DT Shannon Forman returns the interception 25 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Arizona State WR makes spectacular over-the-shoulder grab on 4th down
videos.description: Arizona WR Frank Darby makes a difficult catch on 4th down to bring the Sun Devils into the red zone.

videos.headline: Arizona State scores again before halftime
videos.description: Arizona State QB Manny Wilkins finds WR Terrell Chatman in the back of the end zone for an 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Arizona St. RB makes defenders miss on route to end zone
videos.description: Arizona State RB Eno Benjamin jukes and spins away from UT San Antonio defenders to score.
